{"questionId":"28358","questionHtml":"<p>A projectile is launched with a velocity <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi></math> at an angle <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>θ</mi></math> to the horizontal. It reaches a maximum&nbsp;height <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>s</mi></math>. What is the time taken to reach the maximum height?</p>\n<p><br>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo> </mo><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>s</mi></mrow><mi>g</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo> </mo><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mi>g</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo> </mo><mi>sin</mi><mo> </mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mi>g</mi></mfrac></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"28358","referenceCode":"22N.1.SL.TZ0.4","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A projectile is launched with a velocity u at an angle θ to the horizontal. It reaches a maximum height s. What is the time taken to reach the maximum height? A. 2su cos θ B. 2sg C","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"4","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.1 – Motion","Core","Topic 1: Measurements and uncertainties","1.3 – Vectors and scalars","Core","Topic 1: Measurements and uncertainties","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}